<div class="special-report-header">
  <h4>
    Special report:
    <a href="/specialreports?year[value][year]=2015&amp;category=76986">Energy and technology</a>  </h4>
      <div class="special-report-article-list">
      <strong>In this special report</strong>
      <ul class="special-report-article-links"><li class="0 first"><a href="/news/special-report/21639014-thanks-better-technology-and-improved-efficiency-energy-becoming-cleaner-and-more">Let there be light</a></li>
<li class="1"><span><span class="active">We make our own</span></span></li>
<li class="2"><a href="/news/special-report/21639018-solar-giving-hundreds-millions-africans-access-electricity-first">A brightening continent</a></li>
